  levelNumber: 1
  levelName: Edzna
  location: Campeche, Mexico
  levelDescription: "The stones remember \u2014 even when the world forgets.\n\nA
    Legacy in Stone\nOnce a major Maya city, Edzn\xE1\u2019s name \u2014 \u201CHouse
    of the Itzaes\u201D \u2014 still echoes through its ruins.\n\nHighlights\nGreat
    Temple: 40-meter pyramid overlooking the plaza\nBall Court: Parallel walls marking
    the site of sacred games\n\nTimeline\n400 BC: First settlers\n200 AD: Height
    of power\nInfluenced by Calakmul and Puuc styles\n~1500 AD: Abandoned\n\nRediscovery\nFound
    in 1907, excavated in 1958, and restored in 1986 with international support."
